        </p>

        <div class="news__author_add">
            <textarea  id="textareaAuthor" rows="5" placeholder="Username" ></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="news__comment_add">
            <textarea  id="textarea" rows="5" placeholder="Comment" ></textarea>
            <button id="button">
                Add comment
